    <section name="ExceptionRedirectorValve">
      <subsection name="Description">
        <p>
        The pipeline processing valve which redirect to appropriate view in case the exception occured 
        during pipeline processing. Also it logs the exception according to level set in
        configuration. If no exception was configured it always redirect to 'error_view' and uses
        'error_level' logging level.
        </p>
      </subsection>
      
